'''Koseyet Mining Camp''' was a mining camp on [[Mustafar/Legends|Mustafar]]. It was attacked in [[1 ABY/Legends|1.5 ABY]] by [[HK-47]]'s [[Droid/Legends|droid]] forces as the first part of HK-47's plan to wipe out all "[[Meatbag/Legends|meatbags]]" on Mustafar. It was [[Battle of Koseyet|stopped]] by a group of [[Spacer/Legends|spacers]], however, and Koseyet Mining Camp was saved from destruction.

